             <h2 class="rl_tabs-title nn_tabs-title"><a id="anchor-mres-fees-and-loans" class="anchor rl_tabs-sm-scroll nn_tabs-sm-scroll"></a>MRes Fees and Loans</h2> 
             <!-- START: Articles Anywhere -->
             <p></p>
             <h3>Programme Fees</h3> 
             <p>This programme is only available as a full-time option: part-time study is not possible.&nbsp;</p> 
             <p>Full-time fees;</p> 
             <ul> 
              <li>UK/EU: £11,800</li> 
              <li>Overseas: £25,130</li> 
             </ul> 
             <h3>Postgraduate Loans</h3> 
             <p>UK Government-backed postgraduate loans worth up to £10,280 are now available, to help Masters students cover their tuition fees and living expenses</p> 
             <p>These non-means-tested, repayable postgraduate student loans are similar to those that are offered to undergraduate students, and are a major new development for higher education in England.</p> 
             <p>&nbsp;To find out more and to check if you are eligible visit the governments website:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gov.uk/postgraduate-loan/overview">https://www.gov.uk/postgraduate-loan/overview</a>&nbsp;</p>
